item.title: About Me
item.description: “You only live once, but if you do it right, once is enough.” Hi! I am Lexi Su from China. Welcome to my portfolio website, and here I will introduce myself to you a little more… Some Key Words Passionate Persistent Self-challenger Time-manager “Social Animal” Education I am currently pursuing a Masters Degree in Financial Analysis student at London Business School.
